– Undead hitting the target will be rebuked, taking 1d4+1 magic damage (save vs. Spell to take half) and being forced to flee for 2 rounds if they fail their saving throw vs. Spell. Once affected, they may not be affected again for 1 turn but the damage always apply.

Requires:
 9 Intelligence~

