 @8600 = ~Greater Restoration
(Necromancy)

Level: 7
Sphere: Necromantic
Range: Touch
Duration: Permanent
Casting Time: 9
Area of Effect: Special
Saving Throw: None

When this spell is cast, the life energy level of the recipient is raised. This reverses any previous life energy level drain of the creature by a force or monster. A Greater Restoration spell will also restore the Intelligence score of a creature affected by the Feeblemind spell and negate any form of insanity, such as confusion or berserk. It fully heals the target, cures any diseases or poisons. This restoration spreads to the rest of party members, including the priest, who is healed by half its total health only. The casting of this spell is very draining on the priest, and <PRO_HESHE> will likely require rest immediately afterward. This fatigue is profound, additionally causing a -2 penalty to casting speed, damage, THAC0, and Armor Class, as well as a 35% movement speed penalty for 2 turns.~

